{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mahti iṡdsen/ tas irr beskau-\nnigś un negants Behrns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mittejees mans Behrne\nlo Pamahzifchann klausfht/ kas\nleek malditees no prachtigas Mah-\nzibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weens besdeewigs Leezi-\nneeks apsmeij to Teefu/ un to\nBesdeewigo Mutte eerihj to\nNetatfnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teem Mehdtajeem irr ta\nSohdiba gattawa/ un Kuhleni\npreeksch to Gekko Muggnru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XX. Nodalla.\nMahza ka buhs no leekas Dserichanas un\nPlihteschanas fargatees: 1. Un ka zaar to\nta paʃauliga Waldischana tohp apdujmota/\nBahrshana padarrita/ tas no Deewa us,\nlitks Darbs pamests/ un eegahsch fewi va-\nfchu Nelaimiba ar nclabbahm Runnafcha-\nnahm : 2. etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "As Wihns darra Meh-\nditajus/ stiprs Dseh-\nreens darra Trakgalwi-\ngus/ wiʃs kas ar to eelihgfino-\njahs/ ne taps gudrs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Rehnina Beedinascha-\nna irr ka lahda janua Lauwa\nRuhfschana/ kas pahr winnu\napskaistahs/ tas grehfo prett fa-\nwu Dsihwibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas irr weena Wihra\nGohds no Bahrshanas atkahp-\ntees/ bet wiʃs kas ar to tinnahs/\nirr Gettis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ankstuma pehz ne grib\ntas Slihkis arrt/ tapehz deede-\nlehs wiʃch plaujamá Laiká/ un\nne dabbuhs nenecka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Padohms weena Wih\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "weens prachtigs Wihrs dabbu to\nahra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jkweens Zilweks teizahs\nka wiʃch labba darr/ bet kas at-\nraddihs weenu/ kas pateeti tahds\nirr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Taitnajs staiga alla-\nschix fawa Sirde-Skaidribá/\nfwetigií buhs winna Behrni\npehz winna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weens Kehninsch us fawu\nSohda-Krehslu tehdedams/ is-\ntrenz wiʃfu Launu ar fawahm\nAzzun.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kurjch warr fazzibt : Es\nefinu schkistis fawa Sirde/ es\nefinu skaids no manneem Greh-\nkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Diwejahds Swars un\nDiwejahds Mehrs irr abbi tam\nKUNGAM weena Negantiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir weens Puifs teh-\npee fawas Buhfschanas pasihts/\narrig winna Darbs schkistis un-\ntaisns buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weenn dsirdoschn Ausi-\nun redsign Azzi irr tas KUNgs\nabbejus darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne mthle to Meegu/ ka-\ntu ne tohpi par Nabbagu/ lai-\ntawas Azzis irr mohdrigas/ tad-\ntew Maises gann buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Launs/ tauns fakka tas\nPirzejs: Bet kad wiʃch aifgah-\njis/ tad wiʃch leelijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Daschain irr Selts un\ndaufs Pehrłu/ bet prachtigas\nLuhpas irr weens tohti dahrgs\nGlistums.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
